      <description>&lt;figure class=&#34;responsive-image&#34; style=&#34;margin: 2rem 0; text-align: center;&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;picture&gt;&#xA;      &lt;source media=&#34;(max-width: 600px)&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/posts/the_cycle_of_ai/images/thumbnail_hu_d955b0f56fd6a094.jpg&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;source media=&#34;(max-width: 900px)&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:1313/posts/the_cycle_of_ai/images/thumbnail_hu_aa4673b3d2b6d4bb.jpg&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/posts/the_cycle_of_ai/images/thumbnail_hu_a61ad4d059a0c5dd.jpg&#34; &#xA;           alt=&#34;Meme showing the AI money flow from user to hyperscalers&#34; &#xA;           loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&#xA;           style=&#34;max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/picture&gt;&lt;figcaption style=&#34;margin-top: 1rem; font-style: italic; color: #666; font-size: 0.9rem;&#34;&gt;The AI money cycle: You pay peanuts, they rake in billions. Classic economics, but make it digital.&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;ldquo;You pay a neat little fee for an AI app. That cash takes a theme-park ride: tokens → cloud GPUs → power bill → NVIDIA&amp;rsquo;s earnings call. The only folks sleeping well? The people selling shovels in the gold rush.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
